headline: PsiQuantum Selects Jacobs to Deliver One of the World's First Utility-Scale Quantum Computers in Australia
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was selected by PsiQuantum to deliver master planning, schematic design, and owner's engineer services for what is poised to be one of the world's first utility-scale, fault tolerant quantum computers in Brisbane, Australia.
